ist sarah may poppleton suggested a new type of total contact cast called the tccez® – a total contact casting system total contact casting is considered the gold standard of care for offloading diabetic foot ulcers the tccez® from dermasciences europe is a onepiece rollon woven cast that can be applied in just ten minutes by the podiatrist it works by promoting healing of the wound by minimizing pressure and friction as the tccez® redistributes the weight away from the wounds meaning it can heal even while the patient is walking video of yoojxipzte view all tcc videos references  armstrong dg et al offloading the diabetic foot wound diabetes care    bloomgarden zt american diabetes association th scientific sessions  diabetes care    coleman w brand pw birke ja the total contact cast a therapy for plantar ulceration on insensitive feet j am podiatr med assoc  –   helm pa walker sc pulliam g total contact casting in diabetic patients with neuropathic foot ulcerations arch phys med rehabil –    baker re total contact casting j am podiatr med assoc –   sinacore dr mueller mj diamond je diabetic plantar ulcers treated by total contact casting phys ther –  myerson m papa j eaton k wilson k the total contact cast for management of neuropathic plantar ulceration of the foot j bone joint surg a–   walker sc helm pa pulliam g chronic diabetic neuropathic foot ulcerations and total contact casting healing effectiveness and outcome probability abstract arch phys med rehabil    mueller mj diamond je sinacore dr delitto a blair vpd drury da rose sj total contact casting in treatment of diabetic plantar ulcers controlled clinical trial diabetes care  –   liang pw cogley di klenerman l neuropathic ulcers treated by total contact casts j bone joint surg b–   walker sc helm pa pulliam g total contact casting and chronic diabetic neuropathic foot ulcerations healing rates by wound location arch phys med rehabil –   armstrong dg lavery la bushman tr peak foot pressures influence the 